### BƯỚC A: ĐĂNG NHẬP BẰNG TÀI KHOẢN ADMIN ĐÃ CÓ SẴN TRONG DB/SEED
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

###

### BƯỚC B: ADMIN TẠO TÀI KHOẢN USER NỘI BỘ
### Thay <ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN> bằng token nhận được ở BƯỚC A
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "full_name": "Nguyen Van Thu Nghiem",
    "email": "member.test@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "role": "MEMBER",
    "department_id": 1
}

###

### BƯỚC C: ADMIN XEM DANH SÁCH USER - PAGINATION / SEARCH / FILTER
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=10&search=member&role=MEMBER&status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### BƯỚC D: ADMIN XEM CHI TIẾT USER
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### BƯỚC E: ADMIN CẬP NHẬT THÔNG TIN USER
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "full_name": "Nguyen Van Thu Nghiem Updated",
    "email": "member.updated@gmail.com",
    "role": "PM",
    "department_id": 1
}

###

### BƯỚC F: ADMIN KHÓA / MỞ TÀI KHOẢN USER
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "status": "DISABLED"
}

###

### PROJECT A: TẠO PROJECT
POST http://localhost:5000/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "name": "Internal Task Management",
    "description": "Project test module quản lý dự án",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "start_date": "2026-07-01",
    "end_date": "2026-08-31",
    "manager_id": 1
}

###

### PROJECT B: DANH SÁCH PROJECT - PAGINATION / SEARCH / FILTER
GET http://localhost:5000/api/projects?page=1&limit=10&search=Task&status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_PM_OR_MEMBER_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### PROJECT C: CHI TIẾT PROJECT
GET http://localhost:5000/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_PM_OR_MEMBER_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### PROJECT D: CẬP NHẬT PROJECT
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "name": "Internal Task Management Updated",
    "description": "Đã cập nhật mô tả project",
    "start_date": "2026-07-01",
    "end_date": "2026-09-15"
}

###

### PROJECT E: ĐỔI TRẠNG THÁI PROJECT
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/projects/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "status": "ON_HOLD"
}

###

### PROJECT F: ARCHIVE PROJECT - KHÔNG XÓA CỨNG
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/projects/1
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### PROJECT G: XEM THÀNH VIÊN PROJECT
GET http://localhost:5000/api/projects/1/members
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_PM_OR_MEMBER_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### PROJECT H: THÊM THÀNH VIÊN PROJECT
POST http://localhost:5000/api/projects/1/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "user_id": 2,
    "role": "MEMBER"
}

###

### PROJECT I: XÓA MỀM THÀNH VIÊN PROJECT
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/projects/1/members/2
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### TASK A: TẠO TASK
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "project_id": 1,
    "title": "Thiết kế API Task Management",
    "description": "CRUD task, status flow, assign member",
    "priority": "HIGH",
    "start_date": "2026-07-01",
    "due_date": "2026-07-10",
    "assignee_id": 2
}

###

### TASK B: DANH SÁCH TASK - PAGINATION / SEARCH / FILTER
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks?page=1&limit=10&project_id=1&status=TODO&priority=HIGH
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_PM_OR_ASSIGNEE_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### TASK C: CHI TIẾT TASK
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_PM_OR_ASSIGNEE_JWT_TOKEN>

###

### TASK D: CẬP NHẬT TASK
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "title": "Thiết kế API Task Management Updated",
    "description": "Cập nhật mô tả task",
    "priority": "URGENT",
    "due_date": "2026-07-15"
}

###

### TASK E: ĐỔI STATUS TODO -> IN_PROGRESS
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_PM_OR_ASSIGNEE_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

###

### TASK F: ĐỔI STATUS IN_PROGRESS -> DONE
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_PM_OR_ASSIGNEE_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "status": "DONE"
}

###

### TASK G: ASSIGN TASK
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/1/assign
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>

{
    "assignee_id": 2
}

###

### TASK H: XÓA MỀM TASK
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_OR_MANAGER_PM_JWT_TOKEN>
